ASSASSIN:

        On the first level, climb the left side of the first tree you come
        to, climb to the very top.  Now press 'P' to pause the game and type
        "ACEVIEWFROMUPHEREMATE" and the screens border will flash.  Unpause
        the game and use the following keys:

            '1-6'______Go to corresponding level with infinite energy.
            'W'________________Gives you maximum weapon configuration.
            'E'_______Takes you straight to the end of level gaurdian.
            'C'_____________________________Grants infinite continues.

        Or, on the high score table, enter one of the following:
        "ASSASSIN", "THE ONE THE ONLY", "SUPERFROG", "ALIEN BREED",
        "PROJECT X", "PSIONIC SYSTEMS".  Enter "MIDAN" to continue from
        where you left off.
